أي تعديل في المناطق التالية يتطلب **حماية صارمة**:

**المناطق المحمية:**
- RLS policies (أي ملف في `migrations/` يبدأ بـ `SUPABASE_FIX_RLS_` أو `database/fix-rls.sql`)
- Supabase migrations (`database/migrations/`, `supabase/migrations/`)
- Auth flows (login, register, OTP, MFA, verify-email, password-reset, onboarding)
- `ProtectedRoute` logic
- `PaymentGuard` logic
- PayPal integration (`src/services/paypal*.js`, `src/contexts/PaymentGuard.jsx`)
- CMI integration (`src/services/cmiPayment.js`)
- Orders status transitions (`src/services/ordersService.ts`, `src/features/orders`)
- Payouts (`src/services/payoutService.js`, `src/pages/admin/Payouts.jsx`)
- Refunds (`src/services/returns.js`)
- Edge Functions (`supabase/functions/`)
